{"tid":1817870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年台灣總統選舉及國會選舉討論區","createTime":"2020-01-09T12:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T00:50:14.000Z","uid":281020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"01fe77d7aaa0208e3a89ff966b87316a644d91f9","tid":1817870,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:18:57.000Z","msg":"1月11日就係台灣大選既日子，台灣既總統選舉同國會選舉係同時進行既，所以台灣人會有總統票、區域立委票同不分區域立委票(即政黨票)。<br />\n<br />\n台灣總統大選<br />\n今次有蔡英文、韓國瑜同宋楚瑜(台灣馮儉基)參選。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1b/%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E5%85%83%E9%A6%96%E8%82%96%E5%83%8F%E7%85%A7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F1%2F1b%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2585%2583%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%2582%2596%25E5%2583%258F%25E7%2585%25A7.png&h=d66e4a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡英文當然係為咗連任而參選，佢任內有多番施政失誤，例如一例一休、年金改革，導致民進黨係2018年九合一選舉大敗，佢本人都辭任民進黨主席一職，以承擔敗選責任，而隨住香港反修例運動興起，蔡英文係依一場運動中對中共強硬表態，使到佢既民望由節節上升，台灣人睇到一國兩制下既香港，引發台灣人既「亡國感」。接二連三發生外國同台灣斷交、中共對台灣既威脅、以至台灣經濟如何由依賴中國變成「新南向政策」向東南亞發展，將會係蔡英文連任總統既挑戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6a/%E9%AB%98%E9%9B%84%E5%B8%82%E9%95%B7_%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F6%2F6a%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%259B%2584%25E5%25B8%2582%25E9%2595%25B7_%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2591%259C.jpg&h=68edcd4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國瑜係2018年九合一選舉當選高雄市長，由佢發起既「韓流」帶領國民黨係九合一選舉，使國民黨由頹敗中搵到曙光，主打「高雄發大財」既佢亦有多番爭議，例如韓國瑜在任內質疑民進黨政府阻撓佢發展高雄，亦即「卡韓」，但實際上民進黨政府係有比錢高雄市政府。後來佢係國民黨初選與郭台銘同朱立倫大戰中獲勝，身為高雄市長卻請假參選、在香港議題上進退失據，自居為「庶民」但被稱為「草包」既佢到底會唔會勝得依次選舉呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/04/%E5%AE%8B%E6%A5%9A%E7%91%9C%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD2016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F0%2F04%2F%25E5%25AE%258B%25E6%25A5%259A%25E7%2591%259C%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD2016.jpg&h=969c26b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<del>馮儉基</del>宋楚瑜屢敗屢戰，聲稱今次佢既「終局之戰」，其實大家都知道佢參選係為咗拎選舉補助款，為親民黨拎錢吊命，台灣有相當既一部份人覺得藍綠都係垃圾，可能有抗議票投比佢，台灣選舉有所謂「大雞拉小雞」既策略，即總統參選人為立委參選人助勢宣傳，佢既參選亦對親民黨既國會選舉有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n台灣國會選舉<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7b/9th_Legislative_Yuan.svg/1920px-9th_Legislative_Yuan.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F7%2F7b%2F9th_Legislative_Yuan.svg%2F1920px-9th_Legislative_Yuan.svg.png&h=6ca38382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國會選舉有分區域立委、不分區立委同原住民區域立委，分別有73席、34席同6席。<br />\n<br />\n區域立委同原住民區域立委都係由單議席單票制選出黎，通常係民進黨同國民黨之爭，小黨好難會係依個制度獲勝。<br />\n<br />\n2016年區域立委：民進黨49席、國民黨20席、 時代力量3席<br />\n2016年原住民區域立委：民進黨1席、國民黨4席、無黨團結聯盟1席<br />\n<br />\n不分區立委由比例表制中既並立制選出黎，好多小黨主攻依到，依個制度係「選黨唔係選人」，由政黨制定名單，選民只可能投政黨而唔可以投特定名單入面既某個人，所以亦被稱為「政黨票」，由於採用並立制，依種制度有利大黨、不利小黨，雖然小黨可以係依種制度較易拎到議席，但係並立制既計算方法使大部分議席都係民進黨同國民黨瓜分，亦有5%既得票門檻。<br />\n<br />\n並立制既計算方法：不分區立委既議席總數 X 得票率 = 獲得既議席<br />\n通常大黨都有高得票率，所以係有利大黨。<br />\n假設有100席，A政黨有40%得票率<br />\n100席 X 40% = 40席<br />\n<br />\n2016年不分區立委：民進黨18席、國民黨11席、親民黨3席、時代力量2席<br />\n<br />\n今屆國會最大既關注點係民進黨能否過半、小黨能否突圍而出。國民黨份名單入面有好多親共人物、郭台銘幫親民黨助選，對國民黨既影響有幾大，柯文哲創立既台灣民眾黨目標「藍綠不過半」，幫柯文哲劍指2024年總統大選，泛綠政黨互相搶票會唔會攬炒都係值得我地關注。<br />\n<br />\n選前封關民調(d圖係支那01整既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)：<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e09c34813d12b1ca2b8f94d.jpg/kSXHK7-bfIWFqSPFJNF9rcBaMotzPiR0dQBfF3UAXxc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e09c34813d12b1ca2b8f94d.jpg%2FkSXHK7-bfIWFqSPFJNF9rcBaMotzPiR0dQBfF3UAXxc&h=33091849&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e09a586fd5cc31c9c2b7a11.jpg/_0vw0D1XHcg--LCe8_ILyi1bmh3m5GIgDVDuXg1Q7l4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e09a586fd5cc31c9c2b7a11.jpg%2F_0vw0D1XHcg--LCe8_ILyi1bmh3m5GIgDVDuXg1Q7l4&h=0a764785&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2b78165e6106a0675624854cfc13abff3f5b0aa","tid":1817870,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a706a29bb845b15ca214708e39ea1aa1e1d0dc7","tid":1817870,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:19:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">Twitter組24小時keep住更新</span><br />\n幫手retweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF05MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=fab85feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: red;\">/task</span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"3b2557b24804688319de5b5f27d1e5fcf1759754","tid":1817870,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"星期下午開始睇開票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c3fe29e9ad558e35d59b4ef97e9e1751439e41","tid":1817870,"uid":259674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:25:30.000Z","msg":"咁快開定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f2b6507e5546f938848706f417edcf79d11af5","tid":1817870,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"貼下d台仔圖先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp-wm/s3/media/image/2019/12/08/20191208-034551_U1002_M574912_9ff0.jpg?itok=LlnLIurX\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp-wm%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2019%2F12%2F08%2F20191208-034551_U1002_M574912_9ff0.jpg%3Fitok%3DLlnLIurX&h=bc00f98b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2362f46e9aba59c708308effa229bfb7d1db3976","tid":1817870,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"真心想講蔡英文係贏硬，但係一定唔會好似民調有咁大差距<br />\n<br />\n反而國會選舉好值得去睇，會有幾個情況出現：<br />\n民進黨單獨過半<br />\n民進黨+泛綠政黨過半<br />\n民進黨同國民黨唔過半<br />\n國民黨過半<br />\n<br />\n雖然韓國瑜會輸，但係國民黨d票都係會歸隊，所以國民黨唔會輸咁慘<br />\n反而民進黨會比其他政黨搶票，有可能比國民黨偷雞贏到<br />\n由於不分區有5%選票門檻，泛綠政黨互相搶票可能拎唔5%而拎唔到議席<br />\n仲要睇柯文哲既台灣民眾黨既議席數目，佢既目標係「藍綠不過半」，如果真係「藍綠不過半」，佢就會做關鍵少數影響大局。"},{"pid":"bdf19348b33b2b05982e25cf0fee78298f90ad88","tid":1817870,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b2557b24804688319de5b5f27d1e5fcf1759754","tid":1817870,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:24:20.000Z","msg":"星期下午開始睇開票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:58:12.000Z","msg":"下午4時投完票<br />\n7時差唔多點曬票<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過台灣D媒體點票好鳩<br />\n2004年試過有電視台灌票灌太多<br />\n要偷雞減番D票"},{"pid":"d5a9d0b45dc344ddf7b989867e58c6550230a076","tid":1817870,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:22:33.000Z","msg":"講一講下並立制<br />\n日本同台灣都係用依種制度，雖然佢係比例代表制，但有利大黨<br />\n日本就係因為依種制度造成自民黨長期執政，因為日本人口老化好嚴重，老人人口較多同埋肯去投票，政黨要拎到執政權一定要拎到老人票，結果D政策向老人靠攏，而年輕人點投都係投唔贏班老人，造成年輕人對政治冇興趣。<br />\n<br />\n台灣會用依個制度明顯係要保障民進黨同國民黨既利益啦。"},{"pid":"c6fb9157e3b130b552053cc5796a17a3b271be52","tid":1817870,"uid":276821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:39:07.000Z","msg":"有無香港巴打飛去台北睇大選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40ebdf8a116ee739126b15b974260338c60fb43","tid":1817870,"uid":246835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fb9157e3b130b552053cc5796a17a3b271be52","tid":1817870,"uid":276821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:39:07.000Z","msg":"有無香港巴打飛去台北睇大選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有"},{"pid":"385ca21290837a440cc6bae456b239e2066141fd","tid":1817870,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T00:50:14.000Z","msg":"開始投票啦"}]}